===Etymology===
From the {{inh|en|enm|snaile}}, from the {{inh|en|ang|sneġel}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*snagilaz}}. Cognate with {{cog|nds|Snagel}},
{{m|nds|Snâel}}, {{m|nds|Snâl|t=snail}}, {{cog|de|Schnegel|t=slug}}. Compare also {{cog|non|snigill}}, from {{cog|gem-pro|*snigilaz}}.

